graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Component"
        direction TB
        Proxy["model-registry proxy<br/>(Go REST API Server)<br/>Port 8080/TCP"]
        Controller["model-registry controller<br/>(Go Operator)<br/>Port 8081/TCP health<br/>Port 8443/TCP metrics"]
        CSI["model-registry CSI<br/>(Storage Initializer)<br/>Resolves model-registry:// URIs"]
        Catalog["model-catalog<br/>(Go REST API Server)<br/>Port 8080/TCP"]
        BFF["model-registry-ui BFF<br/>(Go Backend-for-Frontend)<br/>Port 8080/TCP"]
        Frontend["model-registry-ui frontend<br/>(React/TypeScript)"]
        AsyncUpload["async-upload job<br/>(Python Job)"]

        Frontend -->|proxied via| BFF
        BFF -->|REST API calls| Proxy
    end

    subgraph "Watched CRDs"
        ISVC["InferenceService CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io/v1beta1)"]
        CSC["ClusterStorageContainer CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1)"]
    end

    subgraph "Data Stores"
        MySQL["MySQL<br/>3306/TCP"]
        PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP"]
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        HuggingFace["HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
        S3["S3/OCI Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
    end

    subgraph "Platform Services"
        Istio["Istio Service Mesh"]
        KServe["KServe"]
        Dashboard["ODH Dashboard"]
        Prometheus["Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraping"]
    end

    %% CRD relationships
    ISVC -->|watched by| Controller
    CSC -->|registers URI scheme| CSI
    Controller -->|syncs state via REST| Proxy

    %% Data store connections
    Proxy -->|GORM ORM| MySQL
    Catalog -->|GORM ORM| PostgreSQL

    %% External connections
    Catalog -->|fetches model metadata| HuggingFace
    CSI -->|downloads artifacts| S3
    AsyncUpload -->|transfers models| S3
    AsyncUpload -->|downloads models| HuggingFace

    %% Platform integrations
    Dashboard -->|REST API consumer| Proxy
    Prometheus -->|scrapes /metrics| Controller
    Istio -.->|mTLS sidecar| Proxy
    Istio -.->|mTLS sidecar| Catalog
    KServe -->|injects init container| CSI

    %% Kubernetes API
    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"] -->|watch events| Controller
    Controller -->|update labels| K8sAPI

